  "remarks": "\nIn his leadership position as Deputy Minister of Information, Ihar Buzouski is responsible for the repression of civil society, notably with Ministry of Information involvement in cutting off access to independent websites and limiting internet access in Belarus in the wake of the 2020 presidential election, as a tool of repression of civil society, peaceful demonstrators and journalists.",
